definition: to hold/to seize/to catch/to apprehend/to take/(used in the same way as 把[ba3]: to mark the following noun as a direct object)
to obey/to follow/to arrange/to make reasonable/along/favorable

sentences.english: And he that offered his offering the first day was Nahshon the son of Amminadab, of the tribe of Judah
